    "source": "Local faithful reconstruction of the LLM-SRBench LSR-Transform methodology (Shojaee et al., ICML 2025). NOTE: the official llm-srbench HF dataset (239 problems) is GATED and unreachable from this environment; this file reconstructs the LSR-Transform IDEA (rewrite textbook laws into less-common equivalent representations, e.g. solving for a non-standard target variable) so that memorization-resistant reasoning is tested with the SAME API/eval/data protocol. It is NOT the official benchmark and must be labeled as such.",
